==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Billion
<hw>Bil"lion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>billion</ets>, arbitrarily formed fr. L. <ets>bis</ets> twice, in
imitation of <ets>million</ets> a million. See <er>Million</er>.]</ety>
<def>According to the French and American method of numeration, a
thousand millions, or 1,000,000,000; according to the English method, a
million millions, or 1,000,000,000,000. See
<er>Numeration</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Billman</ent>⟦br⟧
